caption:
Meet Dr. Susan, PhD, RN from our connectRN community 💜

Seen here wearing a pair of Encouraging Scrubs from our limited edition @careandwear collection, Dr. Susan is proud to wear and share the message “You make a difference” with other nurses.

“We all have a role to play in nurturing nursing culture to health and protecting it from harm,” she said.

“As a leader working in today's healthcare environment, it’s my duty to foster a culture of respect and inclusivity that welcomes everyone!”

Thank you Dr. Susan for your commitment to encouraging current and future nurses to be the best nurses they can be.

#connectRN #encouragingscrubs #nursesinspirenurses
